                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "8e4f0a27af8441d7b1bd8",
                    "stepText": "Next, consider the effect of the perpendicular magnetic field on the moving ion. Which formula correctly represents the balance between the magnetic force experienced by the ion and the centripetal force required for its circular motion?",
